# https://w3id.org/mlips - MLIPs Ontology
#
# Permanent identifier for an OWL 2 DL ontology describing
# Machine Learning Interatomic Potentials: training datasets with
# DFT/wavefunction-method provenance, MLIP algorithms with their
# hyperparameters and implementations, training runs and trained
# models, and published benchmark results.
#
# Currently redirects to https://onto.degu.cl/mlips/ where the
# upstream server performs Accept-header content negotiation across
# XHTML+RDFa documentation, Turtle, and RDF/XML. The redirect target
# is the maintainer's personal server, used while a University of
# Stuttgart institutional URL is being provisioned. Updates to the
# redirect target must preserve content negotiation.
#
# Submitted as an ISWC 2026 Resources Track paper.
#
# ## Contact
# This space is administered by:
#
# Daniel Hernandez
# daniel@degu.cl (primary)
# daniel.hernandez@ki.uni-stuttgart.de (institutional)
# GitHub username: danielhz

Options +FollowSymLinks
RewriteEngine on

# Bare URL: tools resolve the namespace IRI by stripping the
# fragment, so this is the most common entry point.
RewriteRule ^$ https://onto.degu.cl/mlips/ [R=302,L]

# Path-form URLs: future-proofing for slash-style IRIs and for
# direct file requests like /mlips/mlips.ttl.
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://onto.degu.cl/mlips/$1 [R=302,L]
